&lt;li&gt;Working knowledge of content creation tools - word processing, presentation, image management, etc., and familiarity with content management systems and marketing automation tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrates ability to quickly learn and apply new tools, processes, and standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to explain technical concepts to audiences that have varying degrees of technical ability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong time management skills and an ability to take accountability for completing projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to absorb and retain information quickly, specifically complex technical information&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to analyse target audience and to present ideas in user-friendly language&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interest in telecommunications, VoIP, WebRTC, and voice-bots is an advantage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;The Person:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
