&lt;div class=&quot;ar

&lt;h2&gt;What we offer &lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interact with our clients on regular basis to drive their business towards impactful change.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Seize opportunities at the client and at XYZ in our entrepreneurial environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Become part of a fast growing international and diverse team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Who we are&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are XYZ, We are a dynamic and forward-thinking consultancy firm that operates across a wide range of industries, creating solutions that are tailored to specific needs. We bring long-lasting impact and growth to our partners and clients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With our multidisciplinary teams, we create bold strategies and innovative solutions that are tailored to our client’s needs and help them capitalize on opportunities. Together we strive to bring long-lasting impact and celebrate collective victories.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At XYZ we share an entrepreneurial mindset, a compelling passion to create, and, more importantly, a firm belief in our partnership-driven business model. This is embedded in our culture and safeguarded as we evolve.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our team counts over 450 ambitious professionals with various backgrounds, spread over several continents. Our work environment unifies creative problem-solving and strategic thinking. We provide resources to visionaries who understand the direction in which the world is moving. Tomorrow’s world is data-driven. It is digital. It is international.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Become part of the journey, become part of XYZ. Partners for impact.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What you will do  &lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responsible for the operation and further development of our multi-cloud container orchestration solution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Administer and manage our Linux systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work together with software developers and solution architects to plan, design, test, implement and maintain professional integration solutions in a multi-cloud environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop concepts and methods for automation in a DevOps environment and ensure compliance with processes and documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support with best practices for the scalability, reliability, and performance of our production systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work confidently in a team on escalations and solve critical problems that affect our highly available development, test and production systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Developing and improving standards for security (via security as code) across a continuous delivery environment and cloud-based production deployments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Performance load/stress testing and performance tuning of all tiers including web server, application server, database.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate and report on new tools and techniques for monitoring and securing an e-Commerce site.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;What you’ll bring  &lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8-10 years of Experience in the DevOps field in the Retail &amp;amp; E-Commerce space.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BE/ BTECH/ ME/ MCA- degree in Computer Science, Engineering.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good knowledge of Infrastructure as Code and configuration management, preferably with Terraform and Ansible.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good knowledge of scripting/programming and automation solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Good knowledge of IT operations and security monitoring as well as know-how in CI/CD tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with container technologies (Kubernetes) is an advantage.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong knowledge in DevOps implementation &amp;amp; Practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong knowledge in Azure/AWS/Google Cloud implementation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong knowled

&lt;div id=&quot;header&quot;&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;Devops Engineer&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;jobDetailContainer&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;jobColumn wide&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Als DevOps Engineer maak jij onderdeel uit van Global Client Onboarding team. Binnen GCOB ligt jouw impact bij het vaststellen of klanten voldoen aan wereldwijde wet &amp;amp; regelgeving. Jouw engineering team is dus cruciaal voor de veiligheid binnen de internationale financiële sector.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Je bent werkzaam in een uitdagende en internationale omgeving die gericht is op het aanbieden van klant screening diensten aan wereldwijde gebruikers van het platform. Jij maakt onderdeel uit van een T-shaped DevOps team die digitale ambities realiseert binnen de KYC Area. Dit doe je op technisch gebied met nauwe samenwerking tussen de business en IT stakeholders. DevOps Engineers zijn verantwoordelijk voor stabiliteit, performance van het platform, infrastructuur, security, compliance maar ook innovatie. Jouw inspanningen geven software developers de gelegenheid om zich te richten op hetgeen waar zij in gespecialiseerd zijn.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Voorbeelden uit de praktijk&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Het automatiseren van Azure pipelines in nauwe samenwerking met developers en testers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Een uitdaging welke het team wil realiseren wanneer het platform in de Azure cloud draait is het vernieuwen van het deployment proces van enkele keren per week naar realtime of &#39;when DOD ready&#39;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Het opzetten van goede monitoring op componenten zodat het team in staat is voordat een gebruiker het merkt zaken proactief te kunnen repareren.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Feiten &amp;amp; cijfers&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;36/40 uur per week&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;GCOB is het KYC systeem voor onze wereldwijde license to operate&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Top 3 verantwoordelijkheden&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Je bent gedreven door continious improvement. Je hebt inhoudelijke kennis op het gebied van software omgevingen en automatiseerd handmatige taken zoals deployment, testing en monitoring.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Productiviteit van developers is direct afhankelijk van de system infrastructuur. Jij bent bouwer, automatiseerder en onderhouder hiervan. Dit doe je vanuit het oogpunt stabiliteit en performance. Tot slot houd je ook rekening met security en compliance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;De samenwerking is breder dan alleen de directe collega&#39;s in jouw team. Je bent communicatief vaardig en sterke relaties op met andere technici binnen de Rabobank.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Jij &amp;amp; jouw talent&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Je hebt minimaal 3 jaar ervaring binnen de IT&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Vaardig in zowel de Nederlandse als Engelse taal (woord &amp;amp; schrift)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Inhoudelijke technische kennis van: Cloud oplossingen, Infrastructure-as-code, Docker/Containerization, SQL (Microsoft stack)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Achtergrond in programmeren/ scripten (PowerShell, .NET, Bash)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;(Softskills)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dit bieden we jou&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Een bruto salaris van € 3.292,21 tot € 5.437,98 (schaal 8 of 9)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;dertiende maand en 8% vakantiegeld&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;extra budget van 9%, 10% of 11% van jouw

&lt;p&gt;DublinCo is looking for an&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Account Manager&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;to join our team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Account Management organization is in charge of driving customer retention, growth and expansion opportunities, and continued product optimization and adoption. As an AM, you will own the renewals and upselling of new products into our rapidly growing ecosystem of customers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will not only ensure a premium experience for our customers by understanding their business objectives, but also partner with our Customer Success, Marketing, Product and Finance teams to streamline workflows and communication processes within Greenhouse.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who will love this job:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;strategic hunter,&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;you thrive in a dynamic environment, and clearly see the full picture of an account, always recommending the best solution for both customers and Greenhouse that ultimately drives revenue&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;thoughtful mediator,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;you&#39;re consultative, receptive and authentic through tough situations and hard-to-close negotiations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;collaborative teammate,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;you love working with others and utilizing strong partnerships to achieve the best outcome, whether internal or external&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;hardworking problem solver,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;you&#39;re not afraid to test, iterate, and chip in ideas when it comes to solutions. You roll with the punches and can adapt, but are excited to be apart of the fix&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effectively manage a book of mid-market business totaling up to $5MM in ARR or SMB business totaling up to $2.6MM in ARR&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build strategic account plans that map out expansion and other upsell opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain an active pipeline of forecasted renewals and expansions to meet quota objectives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Customer Success Managers for shared management of your customer relationships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Position yourself as a strategic partner to key stakeholders and champions within named accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continued assessment of Greenhouse’ alignment with customer’s business objectives and goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Actively focus on expansion and growth through identifying, cultivating, and selling additional products within the Greenhouse Suite&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Diagnose and mitigate churn risk clearly and own resolution strategies, advising sales leadership of ideal resolutions wherever appropriate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be an active participant in building and improving internal operational processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You should have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in sales/account management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional verbal, written, and presentation skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent time and process management skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven success identifying and developing executive relationships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The ability to craft narratives and prove customer value through comprehensive business reviews and strategic touch-points&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience handling complex commercial processes and negotiations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Quota carrying experience (e.g., Renewals, Sales, Account Management), preferably in a SaaS organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your own unique talents! If you don’t meet 100% of the qualifications outlined above, tell us why you’d be a great fit for this role in your cover letter&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pay, Perks &amp;amp; Such:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Greenhouse, we love to celebrate our divers

&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.greenhouse.com/mission&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;mission&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;at Greenhouse is to make hiring work for everyone – so we go to great lengths to hire great people because we believe that they’re the foundation of our success. At Greenhouse, you’ll join a team that collaborates purposefully, fosters inclusivity, and communicates with transparency and accountability so we can achieve our mission.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join us to do the best work of your career, solving meaningful problems with remarkable teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;Greenhouse is looking for a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Senior Manager, Sales (Mid Market &amp;amp; Enterprise)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;to build and lead our new-business team in the UK — our fastest-growing market in EMEA. You&#39;ll lead a team of Account Executives selling into mid-market and enterprise across the UK, coaching them to success, selling complex deals and helping them close.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal&quot;&gt;We&#39;re the hiring platform for companies that treat talent acquisition as a competitive advantage — brands like Gong, Hubspot, Tripadvisor and HelloFresh trust Greenhouse as their unified hiring platform. In the last year we&#39;ve shipped a wave of platform innovation and acquired a Voice AI company to go further for a demanding customer base. We&#39;re 14 years in and still building: some weeks are brilliant, some are hard, the playbook isn&#39;t finished, and that&#39;s part of the job.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who will love this job&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A hands-on, customer-centric leader&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;– you coach from inside the deals, not above them, and you want to be in the room when it matters&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A builder&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;– you&#39;re energised by a blank page and want to shape the UK playbook rather than inherit a finished one&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A hunter&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;– you generate pipeline proactively and don&#39;t wait for marketing to fill the funnel&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A people developer&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;– you get a genuine kick out of growing AEs and taking them to a new level&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A connector&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;– you partner naturally across marketing, SDR, partnerships and customer success to win as one team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;An in-market presence&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;– you want to be out with customers and in the community, building Greenhouse&#39;s name in the UK&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Lead, coach, and develop a team of Account Executives selling mid-market and enterprise new business across the UK&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Get into the deals — join key customer meetings, navigate complex stakeholder environments, and help your AEs close&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Build and run a proper outbound motion alongside
